Following quotas set forth in above-mentioned table: lard 10491
                                metric quintals; celluloid in bars, strips or sheets 5 metric
                                quintals; worked celluloid unspecified 10 metric quintals;
                                superphosphates (item 715 a 1) 69 tons;
                                brushes of animal fiber described under tariff item 914 b 2—5 metric quintals.
